\c 6 
\m \bd Faarfannaa \bd*\bd 6\bd*
\s2 \bdit \zbr\bdit*Kadhata Gargaarsa Yeroo Rakkinaa (Geggeessituu warra faarfatootaaf; kun mi'a ribuu qabuun toora saddeettaffaa irratti faarfatame; faarfannaa Daawit)
\m \bd 1\bd* Yaa Waaqayyo, aarii keetiin ana hin ifatin! Dheekkamsa keetiinis ana hin adabin.
\m \bd 2\bd* Anaaf gameera, ati anaaf oo'i yaa Waaqayyo! Namummaan koo guutummaatti roqomeera; ati na fayyisi yaa Waaqayyo!
\m \bd 3\bd* Lubbuun koos immoo baay'ee raafameera, ati garuu yaa Waaqayyo, hamma yoomiitti turta?
\m \bd 4\bd* Yaa Waaqayyo, deebi'i, jireenya koos anaaf oolchi, gaarummaa keef jedhiitii na gargaari!
\m \bd 5\bd* Erga du'ee namni si yaadatu hin jiru, iddoo lafa jalaa keessaa immoo eenyutu si galateeffata?
\m \bd 6\bd* Ani aaduu kootiin dadhabeera, halkanuma dhuftu boo'uu kootiin siree koo nan tortorsa, iddoo ciisicha koo irras imimmaan nan lolaasa.
\m \bd 7\bd* Iji koo gadda irraa kan ka'e arguu dhabe, sababii warri na cunqursan hundinuu na gaddisiisaniifis, dadhabaa in adeema.
\m \bd 8\bd* Waaqayyo sagalee boo'icha koo dhaga'eera'o, isin warri hamaa hojjettan hundinuu ana irraa fagaadhaa!
\m \bd 9\bd* Waaqayyo waammata koo dhaga'eera, Waaqayyo kadhata koo in fudhata.
\m \bd 10\bd* diinonni koo hundinuu in yeellaasifamu, sodaadhaanis baay'ee in raafamu; isaan of irra in garagalu, achumaanis in yeellaasifamu.
\b 
